{"tid":2283013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"區議員許銳宇被控阻差辦公 官質疑警可能被自己人打中","createTime":"2020-11-12T09:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T11:05:09.000Z","uid":56115,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"157a7da0e44bdcc06484992e2f7623270340c537","tid":2283013,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"署理主任裁判官溫紹明看完事發片段後指，事發時有很多揮動動作，包括警員揮動警棍，質疑警長「其實你都唔知自己俾咩打中」，「要制服捉住佢（示威者）咪得，唔使揮棍嘛」。<br />\n<br />\n沙田翠田選區區議員許銳宇（31 歲），被控於去年 7 月 14 日在新城市廣場一期中庭，故意阻撓正在執行職務的警務人員，即警署警長葉克勤。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續指，事發時有示威者向地面射水，被告或因站不穩，故在警長衝向他追捕被告時不及反應過來；警長稱有可能，亦同意被告當時並無參與拉扯該男子。"},{"pid":"958c57c452ac08f8b3525a88b746566c191ad650","tid":2283013,"uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/7-14-%E6%96%B0%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%BF%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A8%B1%E9%8A%B3%E5%AE%87%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%B7%AE%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC-%E8%AD%A6%E7%A8%B1%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E9%98%BB%E6%8B%98%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9-%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E9%98%BB%E7%A4%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-14-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B7%25BF%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E9%258A%25B3%25E5%25AE%2587%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%25B7%25AE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%25AB%2594%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%258B%2598%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E9%2598%25BB%25E7%25A4%2599%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BytVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=a85f844e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F7-14-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B7%25BF%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A